# Hidden Izakaya Website - Implementation Plan

## Goal Description
Create a one-page branding website for a "Hidden Izakaya" (Kakurega).
The site needs to convey **"Sophistication," "Privacy," and "Seasonal Gastronomy."**
Design should be dark, elegant, and use vertical text (tategaki) where appropriate to emphasize Japanese tradition.

## User Review Required
- **Design Vibe**: "Japanese Modern". Dark background with subtle lighting effects.
- **Content**: Focus on the atmosphere (private rooms), seasonal ingredients, and sake.

